  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/1faa7d0b3d074ebdc5c52b0ed824f4eb.avif?t=1749034328\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/8d33d4a7c49c304a703d7fafb2f82af6.poster.avif?t=1749034328\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/8d33d4a7c49c304a703d7fafb2f82af6.webm?t=1749034328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/e5ad4abc4c98b2df8638cc328332db6a.avif?t=1749034328\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ayame is a beautiful young girl from Ryuugai (Japan) that is living a carefree life in search of happiness. One fateful day, she met Robert, a CIA agent who was in Ryuugai during a mission. They become engaged and she moves to Heaven City (USA) with him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When she arrives in Heaven City, she realizes she needs to do her best for the relationship to work. You decide the fate of Ayame in this Slice of Life RPG by Heaven Studios making their Steam debut, and Kagura Games' first Western published game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Slice of Life RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic Storytelling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contemporary Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make Your Own Decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast Travel</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/1faa7d0b3d074ebdc5c52b0ed824f4eb.avif?t=1749034328\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/8d33d4a7c49c304a703d7fafb2f82af6.poster.avif?t=1749034328\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/8d33d4a7c49c304a703d7fafb2f82af6.webm?t=1749034328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184890/extras/e5ad4abc4c98b2df8638cc328332db6a.avif?t=1749034328\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ayame is a beautiful young girl from Ryuugai (Japan) that is living a carefree life in search of happiness. One fateful day, she met Robert, a CIA agent who was in Ryuugai during a mission. They become engaged and she moves to Heaven City (USA) with him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When she arrives in Heaven City, she realizes she needs to do her best for the relationship to work. You decide the fate of Ayame in this Slice of Life RPG by Heaven Studios making their Steam debut, and Kagura Games' first Western published game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Slice of Life RPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic Storytelling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Contemporary Setting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make Your Own Decisions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast Travel</p></li></ul>",
